4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential programming skills in JavaScript and Python. Over 18 weeks, participants engage in hands-on learning, aiming to gain expertise in web development, algorithm scripting, and app creation using front-end libraries and APIs. The program includes three classes weekly, with a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is required, and classes are available in English and Spanish. Upon completion, graduates earn a Full-Stack Developer certificate and enhance their employability in the tech industry. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop